name: Fortune Lady Fire
desc: This card's ATK and DEF are equal to its Level x 200. During each of your Standby Phases, increase the Level of this card by 1 (max 12). When this card is Special Summoned in Attack Position by the effect of a "Fortune Lady" card Target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; destroy that target, and if you do, inflict damage to your opponent equal to that monster's ATK on the field.
